; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 240-242
; Tests saw_cost = true detection in the two-commodity finalize path.
; When a posting has an explicit cost (@ price) without POST_COST_CALCULATED,
; the code sets saw_cost = true and breaks out of the loop, skipping
; the automatic per-unit cost calculation.

2024/03/01 Buy Foreign Currency
    Assets:EUR            200 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Checking

test bal
               $-220
             200 EUR  Assets
               $-220    Checking
             200 EUR    EUR
--------------------
               $-220
             200 EUR
end test
